title: BRIEF-Air Canada Reports Computer-Telecommunications Issues Resolved
text: March 12, 2018 / 7:15 PM / Updated 11 minutes ago BRIEF-Air Canada Reports Computer-Telecommunications Issues Resolved Reuters Staff March 12 (Reuters) - Air Canada: * AIR CANADA REPORTS COMPUTER-TELECOMMUNICATIONS ISSUES RESOLVED AND OPERATIONS RETURNING TO NORMAL * AIR CANADA - RESOLVED COMPUTER-TELECOMMUNICATIONS ISSUES , BUT THERE WILL BE DELAYS & SOME CANCELLATIONS DUE TO OUTAGE Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
